」要求，重点做好四项工作： 一是稳定外部货源。进一步加强与省外蔬菜产地的对接，确保外部货源稳定有效供应。西安市商务局：「买菜难」等主因是企业员工到岗率低，已有措施"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b0ac765776b9b038fe24e3aea93acc21_720w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "82 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/508993342"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IsoD76p3p26U2EAMaCDc1MzkxMDE0IJzhsI4GMBk44QJAJXIJNTA4OTkzMzQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "38_1640855289.3046021", "card_id": "Q_505406730", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 45}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如果让你评选 2021 华语乐坛十大金曲，你会选择哪些有品质的好歌？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "腾讯音乐集团 Tmea 盛典宣布华语十大热歌，包括《白月光与朱砂痣》《浪子闲话》《可可托海的牧羊人》等歌曲，网友纷纷表示华语乐坛开倒车，重返彩铃时代神曲审美。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-c4920dce8993bb60e84032c51a986dc8_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "77 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/505406730"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IsoD76p3p26U2EAMaCDc0NTkzOTM4IMar040GMAE4bEAmcgk1MDU0MDY3MzB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "39_1640855289.3051727", "card_id": "Q_504123904", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 47}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2021 年哪个演员的演技让你一下「爱住了」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-4ce26e406df59413fe6fc0d5f66d4ea7_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "71 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/504123904"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IsoD76p3p26U2EAMaCDc0MzA4MzY1IP+5t40GMAM4RkAncgk1MDQxMjM5MDR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "40_1640855289.3056161", "card_id": "Q_50194561", "feed_specific": {"answer_count":